  <div class="w-full max-w-full mt-4 prose prose-xl">We're leading toward the beta release of bonfire social. Do you feel brave enough to setup a bonfire instance and play with it? <a class="link" href="/docs">Read our getting started guide</a>. Do you want to be involved in our meetings and discuss with us, <a class="link" href="https://matrix.to/#/%23bonfire-networks:matrix.org">join our matrix channel</a>.</div>
